talent level 10 upgrade Sunder
increase health damage by 3%
increase armor gain by 0.2
increase Movespeed gain by 3
increase Evasion gain by 0.20%
remove mana cost

add a new modifier Soul Breaker
After Casting Sunder on them, they will start to lose 1.0% of their max life per second 0.2% on bosses for 5 seconds and Xorn will heal
for that health they lose and every 2% health stolen will further increase the duration of Sunder buff by 0.4 seconds. the health lost
over 5 seconds will not gain any bonus from sunder its self but giving Xorn 1% damage reduction for every seconds of the debuff on the
enemys, the damage reduction buff will last 4.5 seconds and will refresh every time it damage the target (max of 7% damage reduction).
Enemys affected by Soul Breaker will be Passive Break and have 15% reduce healing effect and regeneration as well for its duration.
Xorn will also deal 25% increase damage with any source of damage he does on targets affected by Soul Breaker and having 10% chance to
fear them for 0.4 seconds.

SPELL E Speed Blast
While Xorn is in True Form, he will gain Speed Blast dealing insane damage to a target rooting them and greatly reducing their attack
speed for the Root duration. Speed Blast will also have 15% chance to gain 10% 15% 20% 25% increase damage on its cast. Speed Blast
will also gain 5% 7% 9% 11% of Xorn total movespeed into bonus damage. The Root duration will gain 0.1 duration increase for every 200
Movespeed Xorn has. Speed Blast will always Ignore some armor off the target.

Base damage 18 22 26 30 plus 20% of Agility
Root duration 0.4 0.5 0.6 0.7
Attack speed lost 60 90 120 150
Armor Ignore 3 6 9 12
coldown 15 14 13 12
mana cost 25 40 55 70 plus 1% of max mana

